snippet.title: GensoKishi Online | Sneak Peak into Development! Super Rough Edit #1
snippet.description:
Just before our listing we wanted to share with you the latest development footage to our community members. We put this together overnight so please mind the *rough* edit, BUT this is how much we’ve been working on Gensokishi. It’s coming alive! Can you see it?
We hope you’re just as excited as we are. We’ll get back with you for a super cool edit very soon!!
